Meghann Haldeman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meghann_Haldeman 0 Meghann Michelle Haldeman is an American actress. She was nominated for best juvenile actress for her participation in the series: Camp Wilder (1992), Harts of the West (1994) and The Home Court (1996).
